export default function Lessons() { return (

Study Outline of Revelation

In 7 Lessons we will look at the Book of Revelation divided into 21 (A-U) parts.

Lesson #1 [1-3]:

(A) Introduction

(B) Christ and the 7 Golden Candlesticks

(C) 7 Letters to 7 Churches

Lesson #2 [4-8:1]:

(D) Vision of the Throne

(E) Who is Worthy to Open Book of Seven Seals?

(F) Opening of the 7 Seals

(G) 144,000

(H) Innumerable Redeemed

Lesson #3 [8:2-13; 9-11]:

(I) 7 Angels and 7 Trumpets

(J) Measure the Temple of God

(K) 2 Witnesses

Lesson #4 [12-13]:

(L) Sun-clothed Woman

(M) 2 Beasts and the Dragon

Lesson #5 [14-18]:

(N) FIX CHAPTER ORGANIZATION 14-18 here and belowFall of Babylon

(O) 7 Last Plagues in Vials

(P) Mystery Babylon

Lesson #6 [19-20]:

(Q) The Marriage and Marriage Feast of the Lamb

(R) Millenial Kingdom

(S) Last Judgment

Lesson #7 [21-22]:

(T) All Things New

(U) Closing

) }
